BL09 experiment data processing workflows for tomography and spectroscopy 
processing.

The goal of this project is to create different workflows in order to process
the Mistral data. This should ease the scientists work.

Following scripts should make part fo this project once finished.

- norm2recons (old fastrecons: DONE)
- txrm2recons (from raw data to recons)
- hdf52recons (from raw data in hdf5 to recons)
- ali2recons (from aligned to recons: DONE)
- txrm2norm (from txrm to normalized)








